## Rollout Recommendation

> [!WARNING]
> Don't deploy all tiers at once. Roll out in phases and monitor [server.log](file:///c:/BatchHost-Pro/logs/server.log) for false positives.

1. **Week 1**: Deploy `critical` tier on `/api/auth/login` only + brute-force lockout
2. **Week 2**: Add `agent` tier to agent endpoints — monitor for heartbeat 429s
3. **Week 3**: Add `standard` tier to data APIs
4. **Week 4**: Add `relaxed` tier to page routes

Monitor `RATE_LIMIT` log entries after each phase. If legitimate users/agents are hitting limits, tune the `RATE_TIERS` values up.

